title: Grateful Dead Live at Madison Square Garden on 1987-09-20
lineage: MAC > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 > Wavelab > TLH > FLAC 2448 tagged. Transfer by Andrew F. 09/2011
description:
Set 1

Finiculi Finicula, Addam's Family, Jack Straw-> West L.A. Fadeaway, My Brother Esau, Far From Me, It Must Have Been The Roses, Desolation Row, Might As Well-> Promised Land

Set 2

Hell In A Bucket, Iko Iko, Looks Like Rain-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Throwing Stones-> Not Fade Away, E:Touch Of Grey-> Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text:
Super Dead Encore un concert d'excellente qualité! Le Dead est le meilleur!

J'apprécie Jack Straw et Désolation Row; Phil Lesh est au mieux.

Que du bonheur d'écouter tous ces musiciens
